				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">I am epic!!!<a name="66038"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 8 04 1:46 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Very cool to have my epic item. Did it all   in less then a month, but my bard is 5 years old, and is only 53. This week end I am moving him to his own acount to box him with my pally and druid. I live on Rallos Zek been my home since '99. If anyone has any question about the mobs feel free to post here or e-mail me at: Grimpaladin@yahoo.com . Or stop in on Rallos. You can find me there most times. names: Grimance, Unkempt and or Grimdreamer.
<br />
All mobs where killed with 1 group. Except the scales. We broke into fear with 2 toons. Ran cleric in  to argo see inv mobs, and then SK went in and cleared the zone in. And the group had 4 people under lvl 56. Sk and druid both 65 and ubber.
<br />

<br />
Undead bard: Killed with 7. 53 bard, 65 mag, 2 65 druids, 65 sk, 65 chanter, 65 cleric. Undead bard droped fast. Trak was tricky. You have to have a mag with Call of Hero (CoH) ( I boxed the mag/druid/bard.) Friend boxed the chanter/cleric and other 2 are good friends. You have to have Pureblood on the druids. Very important. And I was chain casting CoH. And the druids tanked some. But being timed gear rules. Best bet is to keep mag on the path up to  the spawn point outa sight of track. mag dies it can get tricky. at 10% My 3 toons went down and Sk and other druid was banished. Buddy with cleric logged off and loaded his rog up and finished the mob. After a pat on the back and rezzings HE mqed the guts. Yes they can be mqed.  
<br />
The only camped that sucked was Eldrig. 12 hours I camped the PH  spot. Took a bard friend of mine 20 mins to find the PH for me. Average spawn time was 14 mins. Thank Gwad for Play Station 2.
<br />
Phinny : killed him 5 times notta. Buddy  of mine killed him and they droped. Mqed. 
<br />
BW guts: found the PH in about 15 mins. Took about 45 mins. Spawns are 90 sec.
<br />
OOT: LoL now that was fun. 53 bard, 53 monk, 54 ranger and 65 druid. We pulled 5-10  cyclops at a time and was tearing it up. Was a blast. about 45 mins to spawn him.
<br />
KC:About two hours. Used my Pally there for tanking. While we waited on the 18 min respawn  time i would train about 5 mobs from all over on us. Got some cool loots. 3 warlords  with nothing. 4 th one had it.
<br />
Dragons: Kileld them a few times  on raids lost rolls. I bot the white scales for 10k and a friend gave me the Red. Took me a week to get the white for 10k. Peeps was selling for 50K. Now way was I going to pay that. I just kept shouting in zones I was in for a week and got a few tells. min was 20 k. then 2 days ago bam! 10K.
<br />
Hmmm I am at work so not sure if I am leaving any drop  out....  Well, this is just my 2 cents from a fresh mind that did it under a month.
<br />

<br />
Grimdreamer,
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
